      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish completely free of any stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear or creasing. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates perfectly, and the engine bay is spotlessly clean. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in 'as-new' condition.",
